                "r": 255,
                "textB": 0,
                "textG": 0,
                "textR": 0
              },
              "comment": "The following event resets a timer while the player is on a platform and running.\nThis allows for adding a \"Coyote Time\" style jump, which can be seen down in the transitions sections of this state.\nThis event is ONLY in the running state, to ensure it doesn't impact situations where a player is knocked back into mid-air, or on a crumbling platform.\nTo ensure that it doesn't get reset when the player is up against a wall and falling, it checks that the player is not jumping nor falling."
            },
            {
              "type": "BuiltinCommonInstructions::Standard",
              "conditions": [
                {
                  "type": {
                    "value": "CollisionNP"
                  },
                  "parameters": [
                    "HeroHitbox",
                    "Platform",
                    "",
                    "",
                    ""
